import { 
    Flex, 
    Box,
    FormControl,
    Input,
    FormHelperText,
    Button,
    Text,
    Avatar,
    Spacer,
    Link
} from '@chakra-ui/react';

const Navbar = () => {

    return (
        <nav h={35} class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
            <Avatar h={85} w={180} borderRadius={50} src="images/logo.png"/>
            <Flex>
                <Text color="blue.200" fontSize="xl" fontFamily="sans-serif" fontWeight="bolder">Home</Text>
            </Flex>
            <Flex ml={50}>
                <Link color="blue.200" fontSize="xl" fontFamily="sans-serif" fontWeight="bold" to="/login">Login</Link>
            </Flex>
            
                <Flex
                    pl={200}
                >
                    <FormControl>
                        <Flex
                        ml={20}
                        flexDir="row"
                        >
                            <FormHelperText color="blue.200" fontSize="xl" mr={20}>Search</FormHelperText>
                            <Input
                            borderColor="blue.200"
                            />
                        </Flex>
                    </FormControl>
                </Flex>
                <Flex
                flexDir="row"
                >
                  
                </Flex>
        </nav>
    
    );
}

export default Navbar;
